  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\">數學遊戲大師-Martin Gardner</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\">我跟家長推薦過幾次的數學遊戲大師-Martin Gardner的著作，非常適合小學生，既有趣又具啟發性！<br />\n<br />\n下面這個著名的魔術「消失的方塊」（Paul Curry發明的）便曾在他的著作中被介紹過，這問題可以「闔家歡樂」一下！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（這個動畫圖在fb中不會動了，我會放在茶會家長群。）</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080304302488832-58bc25da.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/737828967169791/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/737828967169791/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080304302470343-0cbd0ab6.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
